==nowadays_reply==
Sam: What do you spend your time doing nowadays, then? #portrait:sam
Norman: Good grief, it's the same old every day... #portrait:norman
Norman: Wake up, eat, take a stroll to the docks, and watch the fishermen do their thing. #portrait:norman
Norman: Can't do much more than that with these old knees. #portrait:norman
Sam: Wouldn't you like to join them? #portrait:sam
Norman: Gah, if I knew how to fish, maybe I would. I'm far too old to pick up anything new now. #portrait:norman
