==young_advance==
Sam: What was your favorite thing when you were young? #portrait:sam
Norman: Gosh, everyone in this town is a fisherman, but I never picked it up. #portrait:norman
Norman: All my buddies would go to the docks, begging the pros to be apprentices. #portrait:norman
Sam: What about you? #portrait:sam
Norman: Me? I delivered the paper every morning... #portrait:norman
Norman: 40 years on that bike will do a real number on your knees, I tell ya. #portrait:norman
Sam: I see... #portrait:sam
Norman: I like your composure, kid. Show me your catch every now and then. #portrait:norman
Norman: I might not know how to fish, but I know just about everything there is to know about the fish in these waters. #portrait:norman

